            <lg xml:id="TK42">
<l>tuṟantārkkun tuvvā tavarkku miṟantārkku</l>
<l>milvāḻvā ṉeṉpāṉ ṟuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For renunciants, for the destitute, and for the dead,</l>
<l>the one called "householder" is a constant friend.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
